Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,习少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:54.44,DefaultUP,NTP,0,0,0,,您能感觉到什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.38,0:23:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 有三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.80,0:23:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管那家伙发生什么都与我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.54,0:23:59.46,DefaultUP,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要扮成女性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.22,0:24:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是...库因克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.31,0:24:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是十一月十一日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:06.27,DefaultUP,NTP,0,0,0,,三名负责军队的指挥
